{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"format-number","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/format-number","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div>\n<p><code>format-number</code> 함수는 수를 평가하고 제공한 형식으로 그 수를 나타내는 문자열을 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"문법","title":"문법","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">format-number(number ,pattern [,decimal-format] )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"인수","title":"인수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"number\"><code>number</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>형식을 지정할 수</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"pattern\"><code>pattern</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>JDK 1.1 <a href=\"https://java.sun.com/products/jdk/1.1/docs/api/java.text.DecimalFormat.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Decimal Format</a> 클래스 형식의 문자열.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"decimal-format\"><code>decimal-format</code>(선택사항)</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>쓸 수 형식을 정의하는 <a href=\"ko/XSLT/decimal-format\"><code>xsl:decimal-format</code></a> 요소의 이름. 빼면, 기본 decimal-format을 씁니다.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"반환","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>새 형식으로 수를 나타내는 문자열.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"주의","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<p>이 함수는 XPath에 더한 XSLT 고유 추가분입니다. 기본 XPath 함수 라이브러리의 일부가 아닙니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"정의","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#function-format-number\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0 12.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_지원","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"format-number 함수는 수를 평가하고 제공한 형식으로 그 수를 나타내는 문자열을 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"format-number","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"format-number","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"format-number","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xpath/functions/format-number","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/xpath/functions/format-number/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/format-number","title":"format-number"}],"pageTitle":"format-number - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}